# Licenses

This project uses multiple licenses for different components:

## Hardware (CAD files, designs)
**CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Permissive (CERN-OHL-P-2.0)**

See [LICENSE-HARDWARE](LICENSE-HARDWARE) for the full license text.

Applies to:
- All files in `/cad/` directory
- Hardware design documentation

## Software
**MIT License**

See [LICENSE-SOFTWARE](LICENSE-SOFTWARE) for the full license text.

Applies to:
- All files in `/software/` directory
- Test controller application
- Analysis scripts

## Documentation
**Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)**

See [LICENSE-DOCS](LICENSE-DOCS) for the full license text.

Applies to:
- All files in `/paper/` directory
- README and other documentation files

---

For questions about licensing, please contact the author.

